        "cooked": "<p>Usually, in most places, Signal chats are translated to “conversa(s)”. However, in a few places, it just gets ‘transliterated’ and just says chat.</p>\n<p>Example:</p>\n<div class=\"d-image-grid\">\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/e/2/e214ac8bb5409325fe463b8a0bf67f7dc005f537.png\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/e214ac8bb5409325fe463b8a0bf67f7dc005f537\" title=\"Imagepipe_2\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/e/2/e214ac8bb5409325fe463b8a0bf67f7dc005f537.png\" alt=\"Imagepipe_2\" data-base62-sha1=\"wg0cxan9ErQhPBkvkiBf56UKaB9\" width=\"461\" height=\"419\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">Imagepipe_2</span><span class=\"informations\">461×419 28.2 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div><br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/8/b/8bff9adeb286699bda7ab3d9d0a4c2866ee3d4eb.png\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/8bff9adeb286699bda7ab3d9d0a4c2866ee3d4eb\" title=\"Imagepipe_3\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/8/b/8bff9adeb286699bda7ab3d9d0a4c2866ee3d4eb.png\" alt=\"Imagepipe_3\" data-base62-sha1=\"jYtZY3BzLajJFsXsxY1lEJXhyT9\" width=\"461\" height=\"109\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">Imagepipe_3</span><span class=\"informations\">461×109 5.94 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div><br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/c/e/ce73ac3efaea5700247a136c4b25f8fe0cc5fcf4.png\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/ce73ac3efaea5700247a136c4b25f8fe0cc5fcf4\" title=\"Imagepipe_4\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/c/e/ce73ac3efaea5700247a136c4b25f8fe0cc5fcf4.png\" alt=\"Imagepipe_4\" data-base62-sha1=\"tsmbA8AW1tifiNIT3VkWVjyQh1i\" width=\"461\" height=\"267\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">Imagepipe_4</span><span class=\"informations\">461×267 9.24 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div><br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/3/2/32f6e076f180b9697f5f507d811ed81eeae3cb74.png\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/32f6e076f180b9697f5f507d811ed81eeae3cb74\" title=\"Screenshot_20250712-181448\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/3/2/32f6e076f180b9697f5f507d811ed81eeae3cb74_2_225x500.png\" alt=\"Screenshot_20250712-181448\" data-base62-sha1=\"7gQNT6MkVuR6BgnedsNOOKNJKm0\" width=\"225\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/3/2/32f6e076f180b9697f5f507d811ed81eeae3cb74_2_225x500.png, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/3/2/32f6e076f180b9697f5f507d811ed81eeae3cb74_2_337x750.png 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/3/2/32f6e076f180b9697f5f507d811ed81eeae3cb74_2_450x1000.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"212226\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use hr